reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Worked well for a few months until it stopped.
reviews.reviewText: I Bought 2 units in Feb 2023 for me and my daughter. Worked well for a few months until the one that my daughter uses stopped. All Cables we used for our iPhones, iPad n watch still work on my charger but not on my daughter’s now defective charger.I Will need to get her a new one for she’s back in using charger again. She lost all her other chargers and I don’t want her to lose mine coz I always bring this double charger everytime I commute coz it’s real handy with my long cables.I wonder if the seller can still replace the defective one because it hasn’t been a year yet and its life has already expired. 🙏I gave 4 stars. I would like to give 5 stars to all but then the other unit stopped working in less than a year and I had to buy a new one again.
